---
import ClerriLayout from '../../layouts/ClerriLayout.astro';
---
<ClerriLayout title="Channel Strategy" section="channels">

<div class="page-head">
  <div class="page-eyebrow">12 · Channel Mix</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">Foundational, performance, <em>strategic, experimental.</em></h1>
  <p class="page-sub">Four tiers, each with a different ROI conversation. Foundational compounds. Performance pays back. Strategic builds authority. Experimental learns.</p>
</div>

<div class="page-body">

  <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" data-progress-fill="channels"></div></div>
  <p class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)">Progress: <span data-progress-here="channels">0 / 0</span></p>

  <h2>Tier 1 · <em>Foundational</em></h2>
  <p style="color:var(--ink-soft);font-style:italic;font-size:0.95rem">Compounding investments. Harder attribution. Essential. Defends with strategic outcome metrics, not 90-day ROI.</p>
  <div data-section="channels">
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-f-01" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">SEO + content engine — long-form authority, comparison content (already winning DentalHQ/Bento SERPs)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-f-02" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">AEO optimization — structured data, canonical answer content, AI assistant tracking (Otterly → Profound)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-f-03" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Website infrastructure — conversion optimization, lifecycle automation, attribution</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-f-04" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Martech stack — Pardot/Salesforce, attribution, analytics, dashboarding</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-f-05" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">City-page SEO scaffolding for patient directory (AI-generated, human-edited at scale)</div></div></label>
  </div>

  <h2>Tier 2 · <em>Performance</em></h2>
  <p style="color:var(--ink-soft);font-style:italic;font-size:0.95rem">Measurable. Scalable. Adjustable. Defends with payback math. Kill if 90-day ROI hurdle missed.</p>
  <div data-section="channels">
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-p-01" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Paid search (Google, Bing) — $8-15K/mo recommended (see Ad Spend Tiers)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-p-02" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Competitor conquest — Pearly, DentalHQ, BoomCloud, Plan Forward, Subscribili alternative searches</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-p-03" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">LinkedIn paid ABM — top 200 DSO execs, group leaders, owners</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-p-04" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Content syndication — Group Dentistry Now, Becker's Dental, Dental Economics</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-p-05" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Trade shows — ADSO Summit, DEO Intensive, ADA SmileCon (final 2026)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-p-06" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Targeted ABM — top 50-100 DSOs via Common Room / Default signals (skip 6sense)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-p-07" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Retargeting + webinar engine</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-p-08" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Geo-paid Google Ads for patient directory in high-density Clerri metros</div></div></label>
  </div>

  <h2>Tier 3 · <em>Strategic</em></h2>
  <p style="color:var(--ink-soft);font-style:italic;font-size:0.95rem">Category authority. Harder ROI. Critical for credibility — especially with Charlesbank reporting.</p>
  <div data-section="channels">
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-s-01" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Thought leadership cadence — Jim, John (CS), Jacob (product), customers, partners. Out-podcast Comstock + Lohman.</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-s-02" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">PR beyond press releases — co-marketing Sunbit, joint webinars Dental Intelligence, HSO/Planet DDS announcements</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-s-03" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Industry analyst relations — Becker's editorial, GDN editorial; potential Gartner/Forrester for DSO credibility</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-s-04" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Conference speaking across leadership — ADSO Summit, DEO Intensive, GDN Emerging Groups</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-s-05" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Award submissions — Inc. 5000, healthcare innovation awards, Becker's Dental 100</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-s-06" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">"State of Dental Membership" annual report — Hint Health pattern, Year-1 deliverable</div></div></label>
  </div>

  <h2>Tier 4 · <em>Experimental</em></h2>
  <p style="color:var(--ink-soft);font-style:italic;font-size:0.95rem">Run full speed ahead. Jim's explicit "comfortable failing" appetite. Kill quickly when not working.</p>
  <div data-section="channels">
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-e-01" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">TikTok influencer testing — dentists, hygienists, front office. Possibly gamified.</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-e-02" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Short-form social — practice transformations, member savings (Castmagic + Opus Clip workflow)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-e-03" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Podcast strategy — launch Clerri's own OR sponsor GDN Show / Bulletproof / Dental A Team</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-e-04" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Employer channel pilot — TakeCommandHealth + Compt + Fringe marketplaces (SMB)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-e-05" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">$50 demo incentive — segment by role/title (Jim's question)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-e-06" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Patient advocacy / referral programs through practices</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="ch-e-07" data-section="channels" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Dr. Glenn Vo / Nifty Thrifty Dentists "Deal of the Month" — pay-for-deal, 37-57K dentist audience</div></div></label>
  </div>

  <div class="note-block">
    <div class="note-label">Channel performance notes <span class="note-saved">✓ saved</span></div>
    <textarea data-note="channels-notes" placeholder="CAC by channel, what's outperforming, what's being killed, surprise wins..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="topic-foot">
    <a href="/clerri/website"><span class="dir">← Prev</span><span class="name">11 · Website</span></a>
    <a href="/clerri/partners"><span class="dir">Next →</span><span class="name">13 · Partners</span></a>
  </div>

</div>
</ClerriLayout>
